@@TJvDrawPosition
Summary
  Type used to define the position of the caption bar.
Description
  TJvDrawPosition is the type used to indicate the position of the caption bar.
@@TJvDrawPosition.dpLeft
  The caption bar is aligned to left edge of the panel.
@@TJvDrawPosition.dpTop
  The caption bar is aligned to top edge of the panel.
@@TJvDrawPosition.dpRight
  The caption bar is aligned to right edge of the panel.
@@TJvDrawPosition.dpBottom
  The caption bar is aligned to bottom edge of the panel.
